OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774868573
OL,3,CPolice investigating death of man a
OL,4,Cyear after finding bones at recycling
OL,5,Cplant
OL,7,FInvestigations are ongoing into the
OL,8,Fdeath of an unknown man a year after
OL,9,Fhe was found in a recycling plant in
OL,10,FHartlepool.
OL,12,FPolice were called to Tofts Farm
OL,13,FIndustrial Estate on Sunday 30 March
OL,14,F2025 after a number of bones were
OL,15,Ffound by Biffa employees.
OL,17,FAn examination revealed the bones as
OL,18,Fbeing human and following detailed
OL,19,Finvestigation, detectives have now
OL,20,Fconfirmed they are the remains of a
OL,21,Fman.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
