CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774868573
OL,3,CPolice investigating death of man a
OL,4,Cyear after finding bones at recycling
OL,5,Cplant
OL,7,FThe recycling deposited at the plant
OL,8,Fhad come from four areas - Derbyshire,
OL,9,FDurham, East Cheshire and East Riding
OL,10,Fof Yorkshire.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Chris
OL,13,FPringle said: "While it has been one
OL,14,Fyear since the remains of a man were
OL,15,Fdiscovered at the recycling plant, the
OL,16,Finvestigation has been ongoing, and
OL,17,Fthis will continue in the year ahead.
OL,26,@uD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
