OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1774868573
OL,3,CPolice investigating death of man a
OL,4,Cyear after finding bones at recycling
OL,5,Cplant
OL,7,F"In that time, we have sought
OL,8,Fspecialist advice and expertise, both
OL,9,Fhere and overseas, working closely
OL,10,Fwith organisations such as the
OL,11,FNational Crime Agency and developing
OL,12,Fon the forensic work.
OL,14,F"An investigation such as this is
OL,15,Fextremely complex and will continue to
OL,16,Ftake a considerable amount of time to
OL,17,Freveal his identity.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
